To use Zap2It's DataDirect service, the "Grabber Command" must be
changed.

Go to "Tools", "Options", "Advanced" and "Downloading", and change the 
Grabber Command to be:

tv_grab_na_dd --config-file "%misc.grabber_config%" --offset %offset% 
--days 1 --output "%misc.working_directory%/tv-%date%.xmltv"
